<plot>Grace Miller, a well-known actress takes her young daughter Olivia out for a day on the 3rd Promenade in Santa Monica, California. Amidst the crowds of people, Grace notices two men who seem to be following her. When Grace steps into a store for a brief moment, she gets distracted and Olivia suddenly goes missing, sending Grace into a panic in search of her missing daughter.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?130704</url></doc>
